property_description: We are Excited to present this impressive offering; a spacious modern residence, located just 6 blocks from the water and moments away from downtown shopping, culture, and convenience, replete with 180 degree views across the bay. Tri level floor plan, remodeled in 2003 situates the kitchen, dining, formal living and primary suite on the top floor- ensuring that the expansive views of Mt Diablo, Carquinez Strait, and downtown are appreciated from the spaces you use most. Beyond the views, the primary level is simply enchanting. Numerous windows and skylights bathe the interior with light. The result is an open concept floor plan that invites you to spend the day and enjoy yourself. Two sets of French doors open onto the generous top deck. When winter comes and it's time to shutter the doors, three fireplaces offer nostalgia and comfort. The entry level features a reception room and ornate staircase. Also on this floor are two bedrooms, a full bath, laundry and the bottom deck. Finally, the ground floor presents a large family room with yet another full bath and backyard access. Truly a space unto itself, this is the perfect den, media room, or 4th bedroom. Practical conveniences include fully paid off solar. So much to offer.

property_description: Welcome to this enchanting 1940s Bungalow nestled in the heart of the desirable Haans Park subdivision in Vallejo. The home is situated on a charming street lined with majestic sycamore trees. From the kitchen, enjoy a charming view of the beautiful rose garden across the street. Enjoy the picturesque green lawns both in the front and back of the property, providing a serene and inviting outdoor space. Ideal for entertaining guests or relaxing on a sunny afternoon, the pergola adds a touch of elegance and function to your outdoor living area. A spacious backyard offers endless possibilities, including a detached space perfect for a home office or a cozy she-shed. Gorgeous hardwood floors span the home, adding warmth and charm to every room. The inviting living room features a timeless wood-burning fireplace, ideal for cozying up on cold evenings. Sophisticated crown molding enhances the home's interior, providing a touch of elegance. The kitchen boasts a gas-burner stove, making cooking a delightful experience. The newly installed air conditioning system ensures year-round comfort. Take advantage of this unique opportunity to own a piece of Vallejo's history while enjoying modern comforts and an unbeatable location. Don't miss out on this gem in Haans Park!

property_description: Welcome home! Welcome to 50 Castellina Circle, where you will find a beautifully updated and cared for home. Walking through the newly landscaped front yard with lighted path and trees, you enter the home and are welcomed with beautiful Hickory wood floors. The great room is just off the foyer, where the floors really shine and where life happens. In the great room you will find the kitchen, the dining room, the family room, and a great space for entertaining. The center piece of the great room is a massive kitchen island with bar seating, storage, and where memories will be made. Huge windows let plenty of light in through the plantation shutters and a sliding glass door leads you to a private backyard with no rear neighbors. This great layout has 2 bedrooms down one hallway and the primary bedroom on the other side of the home leaving a nice private space. 1 bedroom doesn't have a closet so could be used as a den/office as well. Some updates include solar, Tesla Power Wall, new front landscaping with lighting, new fences and gates, updated guest bathroom, updated flooring, updated appliances, and much more. Come see this beautiful home for yourself and imagine the memories made! This is one home you won't want to let slip by!

property_description: Don't miss out on this opportunity to purchase 6-units on 2-parcels. SELLER FINANCING AVAILABLE (up to 65% LTV @5%) 541-533 Admiral Callaghan is the perfect starter property for investors looking to break into the commercial market. The property consists of four 2-bedroom/1-bathroom apartment units and two 2-bedroom/1.5-bathroom townhouse units. All units are leased at near-market-rate rents. Each unit includes laundry machines, private yards, and tankless water heaters. Ownership has updated select units with new flooring, paint, bathrooms, water heaters and kitchens. The roof has also been replaced within the last ten years. Covered parking is available on-site with one space allotted to each unit(6 total). Vallejo, situated in the San Francisco Bay Area, offers a robust rental market supported by ongoing revitalization projects and excellent transportation links. Its diverse economy and proximity to major highways, public transit, and educational institutions make Vallejo a desirable location. This Vallejo Core location offers close proximity to major employment hubs like Marin, Petaluma, Fairfield, and the East Bay, all at a fraction of the cost.

property_description: This meticulously preserved Mid-century Modern home, in the heart of the Vista de Vallejo neighborhood, offers a captivating glimpse into the elegance and sophistication of the 1950s. The rich mahogany wood paneling sets a warm and refined tone, characteristic of the era's design ethos. The spacious living room, anchored by a grand wood-burning fireplace, exudes both grandeur and comfort, inviting gatherings and relaxation. Throughout the house, gleaming hardwood floors create a seamless flow between rooms. The six bedrooms, bathed in natural light, showcase timeless mid-century design elements. Each of the three full bathrooms features the era's distinctive color palette and design sensibilities. In the kitchen, the 1953 classic linoleum flooring stands as a testament to durability and style. Custom cabinetry enhances functionality, while a cozy breakfast nook provides a perfect spot for morning coffee or tea. The 627-square-foot Rumpus Room, offers a spacious play area and features another large wood-burning fireplace. Descending to the lower level, a custom-built sauna provides a luxurious retreat, while outside, a swimming pool invites relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. For enthusiasts of cars or hobbies, the two massive garages provide space for vehicles, tools, and storage

property_description: 3612-3672 Sonoma Blvd is a stunning 7-suite retail strip building located in the thriving city of Vallejo, California. Situated on two parcels of land totaling 1.65 acres, the subject property was originally constructed in 1977 and has a gross building area of approximately 14, 240 square feet, offering its tenants beautifully designed retail floor plans. As one of Northern California's most prominent small towns, Vallejo features a wealth of culture and attractions including the popular theme park Six Flags Discovery Kingdom, museums, parks, music venues, art galleries, theatres, and a historic, waterfront downtown with a vibrant nightlife. The city's proximity to the Bay Area provides affordable housing to many while boasting a strong economy as more businesses and residents move in. The subject property provides tenants convenient access to major transportation corridors and public transportation, such as the Mare Island Causeway, California State Route 38, California State Route 29, Interstate 80, Interstate 780 as well as many others.

property_description: If hobbits won the lottery and moved to California, this is where they'd live. This Storybook home includes a stone exterior that reminds you to beware of dragons. Even though the architectural style is Provincial Revival there's plenty of modern sophistication too. Fairytale architecture might make you feel like you would meet Hansel and Gretel but what you will find is a stunning living room, remodeled kitchen, loft, vintage bathroom, and a lot of old-world charm. Many renovations throughout the home and yard were done in the last few years including a full kitchen remodel. Be forewarned, you're going to get sick and tired of hearing your guests tell you how beautiful your home is. They'll want to visit every day, so leave a few logs in the fireplace. The stone siding will keep you warm in winter and cool in summer. Vallejo has some of the best weather in the bay. This home is positioned to take advantage of it. Outdoor living awaits. The backyard is private with a decomposed granite patio and a large fireplace. It is not the Shire, but this home is located in a lovely Vallejo neighborhood called Amador. The property is surrounded by Spanish Revival and Tudor homes complete with tree-lined streets. It might seem like a fairytale but this home can be yours (hobbits not included)

Each room is filled with natural light from numerous windows, complemented by 9-foot ceilings throughout. The downstairs area features one bedroom or a den, separate living room with a gas fireplace and French doors leading to your private deck. Down the hall you'll find a spacious and open kitchen with a center island, ample cabinet space and pantry, adjoined by a large family room with a second gas fireplace. This level also includes a full bathroom with a shower stall, an indoor laundry room, and a spacious 2-car garage. Upstairs, you'll find a loft and a spacious primary suite with a tiled master bath, complete with a separate tub and shower. This property is situated between the banks of San Pablo Bay and the Napa River. The island offers breweries and coffeehouses that neighbors can walk or drive to, including Vino Godfather wine tasting, MI Brewery, Savage and Cooke Whiskey Distillery, Quarters Coffee House, and the Vallejo ferry service from the island to San Francisco. Come experience the historic charm and vibrant community of Mare Island!

This well appointed Spanish Mediterranean is 2BR/1.25BA plus an absolutely HUGE basement with high ceilings and separate entry plus a garage plus a workshop plus storage area. Many nostalgic features including a milk door, wainscoting, archways, hardwood floors with in lay, phone niche and a formal entry with a stained glass window. The large, light filled living room has a picture window with a hill view. Formal dining room with built in storage. Kitchen features tile backsplash and a breakfast nook with a built in hutch and an adorable fold down writing desk. Both bedrooms are generously sized with deep closets. The bathroom has subway tile walls, tile floor + a storage closet with a laundry chute. Bonus water closet with cute wallpaper. The basement runs under most of the house and offers a wealth of possibilities as a multi purpose room or possible ADU. Walk through the mudroom to the deck which overlooks the idyllic yard with flowers, lemon and cherry trees and rosemary. 1.3 Miles to the Ferry Building. Conveniently located near freeways, shopping, restaurants, schools, parks and weekly farmer's market. See it today!
Appliances: Free Standing Refrigerator, Free Standing Gas Range

property_description: 1029 Tennessee St in Vallejo is proudly presented by Rosanna Souza from Messina Realty and David Tipp with Tipp Realty at Glen Cove. This freestanding multi-tenant building lends itself for an ad value investment opportunity. The 8650 square feet is hidden behind a subdued facade and the interior is quite surprising with a grand staircase in the middle of the building. The lower floor tenants are a dance studio and massage business with high ceilings in each location. The second level and workshop space on the lower floor is occupied by an administrative medical office. There are additional suites that are vacant to create more cash flow. The building has 3 bathrooms, kitchen and 8 separate spaces. Based on data from the City of Vallejo the traffic count clocks over 14, 000 cars per day at this location. Flexible Zoning with the vacant spaces. The property is also located in an Opportunity zone. Mare Island Development and highway 29 is close to this location for a carry over of opportunities.

property_description: 1609 Lewis Brown Drive is a 3-parcel industrial property located in the northern part of Vallejo, California. The property consists of two buildings on approximately 2.35 acres. The front building is a versatile showroom and industrial warehouse spanning +/-23, 736 SF. It features a loading dock, prominent frontage along Lewis Brown Drive that is perfect for showcasing products, high ceilings, skylights, and an office on the mezzanine level. The back building, covering +/-7, 164 SF, is a light industrial space with a spacious yard and roll up door. There is 400a 3-ph power, ample parking in the front and back, and access to the property via Commercial Street from the rear. The property will be delivered vacant at close. The property's zoning allows for a wide range of uses. 1609 Lewis Brown Drive is located at the intersection of Highway 37 and Highway 29, offering easy access to the entire Bay and visibility to the 91, 000 vehicles that pass by daily. The neighborhood is primarily comprised of industrial facilities and shopping centers. The investment appeal of the property is its convenient location, vacant owner-user potential, and flexible allowable uses.

property_description: A perfect blend of classic charm and modern potential at 613 3rd Ave, Crockett, CA. This unique duplex offers two distinctive living spaces, making it an ideal investment opportunity or a versatile home for an extended family. The upstairs unit features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a balcony overlooking the sport field, authentic plaster and lath, rounded ceiling corners, classic cedar hardwood floors, a living and dining area, and a pantry. The downstairs unit includes 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, a living area, a spacious kitchen, a balcony with a view of a lush green backyard bursting with oranges and lemons, and a utility room excellent for work projects or storage. Additional features include a raised one-car garage located in a separate building and a massive work/storage area underneath the garage, perfect for tradesmen or additional storage. Zoned for 2-4 units, this property offers potential for development and expansion. Located in a quiet neighborhood with ample street parking, it is close to downtown Crockett, which recently opened a new coffee shop. Near the C&H Sugar Plant and Carquinez Strait, this area is rich with trade and commerce opportunities. Embrace the charm, explore the possibilities, and make this versatile duplex your own.

The salon's strategic location, just minutes from Benicia and American Canyon, allows for the capture of a broader customer base, further expanding the potential for growth. Additionally, there is ample room to add your own beauty expertise, enhancing the overall customer experience.

property_description: Motivated seller! Must see the wonderful new updates since property was originally listed. Fresh paint on interior and exterior, brand new laminate flooring in kitchen replaces the old linoleum, and a few unsightly cement cracks have been filled. All 3 bedrooms are spacious and have natural lighting. This lovely Craftsman is located in Vallejo's Heritage District. This absolutely charming, freshly painted home has beautiful laminate floors throughout, ceiling fans, central heat & A/C which is practically unheard of in these beautiful, historic homes. It also has wonderful built-in cabinets for storage and convenience. The updated kitchen has lots of cabinet and counter space. Huge basement/garage area for extra storage space and laundry hookups. Fridge, dishwasher and gas stove are included. The back porch has space for furnishings to relax on those warm summer days. Property is conveniently located just blocks from the Vallejo waterfront with daily ferry service, weekly Farmers Market, and a plethora of restaurants and boutique shopping. All reasonable offers will be considered.
Appliances: Hood Over Range, Gas Water Heater, Free Standing Refrigerator, Free Standing Gas Range, Free Standing Gas Oven, Disposal, Dishwasher

This home is full of its grandeur & pride.

property_description: Incredible Water & Hill Views from almost every room!! Welcome Home to 1364 Bonita Bahia Court with In-Law Potential. This 4 bedroom and 3.5 bathrooms home boasts 3000' square feet. Attractive curb appeal with Batten Board and Shingle siding, beautifully landscaped yard and covered entrance. Open entryway with windows adding character and light. The downstairs features an updated kitchen, stainless appliances and beautiful countertops, a space great for entertaining with an expansive deck accessible from the many sliders throughout. Additional downstairs features include tile and recessed lighting throughout. A beautiful custom artistic staircase leads you to a loft area and additional living space including 2 primary suites, full bathrooms and upstairs laundry. One primary bedroom has an amazing view to enjoy from bay window seating area, hardwood flooring and a primary bathroom with dual sinks, walk in shower, walk in closet and soaking tub. The 2nd primary bedroom is oversized with endless possibilities of an In-Law Unit with a separate entrance and landing, accessible from the backyard, or perhaps a 5th bedroom. You will appreciate the awe of the natural light and custom designs. Terraced backyard includes a greenhouse. Located within blocks of the water and State Park!
Appliances: Microwave, Hood Over Range, Electric Cook Top, Disposal, Dishwasher, Built-In Refrigerator, Built-In Electric Oven

property_description: Welcome to 2664 Avocet in Vallejo. Nestled in a serene cul-de-sac on the golf course, this fabulous 3 bedroom/2.5 bath home (with Solar System!) offers a perfect blend of comfort and sophistication. Step into spacious living areas, including a large living/dining room and family room, as well as an office/den. The spacious kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with granite countertops, an island, and a pantry, providing ample space for culinary adventures. Retreat to the expansive master suite on the main level, complete with a fireplace and two walk-in closets. Venture into the large bonus room featuring a wet bar and access to the lush backyard adorned with a trellis-covered patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Enjoy leisure time on the deck overlooking the picturesque Hiddenbrooke Golf Course. This home also features a convenient 3-car garage. Hiddenbrooke is a beautiful master-planned community just minutes away from the Napa and Sonoma Wine Regions. Surrounded by 700 acres of permanent open space, the new owner will enjoy incredible views along with the signature Arnold Palmer designed golf course.
